location.fullValue: Kamoalii R Plan, The Cottages on Ali'i Drive

data.description: Welcome home to this single level turn-key furnished home with incredible ocean views and a pool!  The spacious screened in lanai makes for a lot of additional living space.  The entire home has tile floors and split zone AC.  The kitchen features granite tops and newer Thomasville cherry cabinetry.  The in ground swimming pool is perfect for doing laps or throwing a pool party!  A maintenance free Trex deck completes the backyard where you can enjoy endless ocean views while you BBQ.  The yard also feature mature fig, orange, plumeria, and hibiscus trees. The location of this home cannot be beat, you're less than 10 minutes from the beach & town and 25 minutes to Costco and the Airport.
